title: Free Week Where Art Thou

embed.description: Greetings Summoners! Here are this week's free champions.

body: Umm, where are the free champs for this week, ingame we are still only able to access last weeks

replies.body: Thanks for the report! There was an issue with the system that changes to the new champion rotation - we've now fixed that up, and you should see the correct rotation shortly.
Yep, they are showing up now, cheers for the reply
